<p>Oralce Linux 7 VM은 다음 링크</p>

<blockquote>
  <p><em><a href="https://blogs.oracle.com/scoter/ansible-with-oracle-linux-virtualization-manager-olvm">https://blogs.oracle.com/scoter/ansible-with-oracle-linux-virtualization-manager-olvm</a></em></p>
